    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>At MathWarriors, we value the privacy of our users. This privacy policy outlines how our app operates and our commitments regarding user data.</p>

    <h2>Collected Data</h2>
    <p>MathWarriors does not collect any personal or device data from users.</p>

    <h2>Ads</h2>
    <p>The app uses the Google AdMob advertising platform. AdMob may display personalized or non-personalized ads to users. For more information on AdMob's data collection practices, please refer to Google's <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>Children Under 13</h2>
    <p>The app is suitable for all age groups, including children. In order to protect children's privacy, no personal data is collected. During ad serving, Google AdMob complies with its policies for child-directed ads.</p>

    <h2>Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
    <p>The app does not share user data with any third parties.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any updates will be posted on this page. Users are encouraged to review the policy regularly.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at: samilasal26@gmail.com</p>
